  <div class="left_article fadeInDown animated">
  <p>This photographic periodic table is composed by 103 images created by students
coming from 25 different high schools in North-East Italy (Veneto
region). The work was developed in the framework of the national Piano
Lauree Scientifiche (PLS, Scientific Degrees Plan) project at the Department
of Chemical Sciences of the University of Padova. <br> The English version was translated from Italian by Francesca De Zotti in 
collaboration with Carlos Alfonso Rivera.</p>
	</div>	  
